msgid "Access Concentrator Name"
msgstr "Ainm an Tiúchantóra Rochtana"

msgid "Both Interface"
msgstr "An Dá Chomhéadan"

msgid ""
"Causes <code>pppoe</code> to exit if no session traffic is detected for %s "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"Fágfaidh <code>pppoe</code> as mura n-aimsítear trácht seisiúin ar feadh %s "
"soicind."

msgid "Client Interface"
msgstr "Comhéadan Cliant"

msgid "Default: 5000"
msgstr "Réamhshocrú: 5000"

msgid "Default: 600"
msgstr "Réamhshocrú: 600"

msgid "Default: 64"
msgstr "Réamhshocrú: 64"

msgid "Default: hostname"
msgstr "Réamhshocrú: óstainm"

msgid ""
"Each one causes the named service to be advertised in a Service-Name tag in "
"the PADO frame. The first one specifies the default service, and is used if "
"the PPPoE client requests a Service-Name of length zero."
msgstr ""
"Déanann gach ceann díobh an tseirbhís ainmnithe a fhógairt i gclib Ainm "
"Seirbhíse i bhfráma PADO. Sonraíonn an chéad cheann an tseirbhís "
"réamhshocraithe, agus úsáidtear é má iarrann cliant PPPoE Ainm Seirbhíse ar "
"fad nialasach."

msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Cumasaithe"

msgid "First remote IP"
msgstr "An chéad IP cianda"

msgid "Grant UCI access for luci-app-rp-pppoe-server"
msgstr "Deonaigh rochtain UCI do luci-app-rp-pppoe-server"

msgid "IP of listening side"
msgstr "IP an taobh éisteachta"

msgid ""
"If specified as <code>0.0.0.0</code> remote IP allocation will be delegated "
"to <code>pppd</code>"
msgstr ""
"Má shonraítear é mar <code>0.0.0.0</code> déanfar ciandháileadh IP a "
"tharmligean chuig <code>pppd</code>"

msgid ""
"If specified as <code>0.0.0.0</code> the selection of local IP address is "
"delegated to <code>pppd</code>"
msgstr ""
"Má shonraítear é mar <code>0.0.0.0</code> déantar roghnú an seoladh IP "
"áitiúil a tharmligean chuig <code>pppd</code>"

msgid ""
"Instead of numbering PPPoE sessions starting at 1, numbering starts at %s"
msgstr ""
"In ionad na seisiúin PPPoE a thosaíonn ag 1 a uimhriú, tosaíonn an uimhriú "
"ag %s"

msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Comhéadan"

msgid ""
"Interface from which to relay. Only PPPoE clients may be connected to this "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Comhéadan ónar féidir sealaíocht a dhéanamh. Ní féidir ach cliaint PPPoE a "
"nascadh leis an gcomhéadan seo."

msgid "Interface on which to listen."
msgstr "Comhéadan chun éisteacht leis."

msgid ""
"Interface on which to listen. Only PPPoE servers may be connected to this "
"interface."
msgstr ""
"Comhéadan chun éisteacht leis. Ní féidir ach freastalaithe PPPoE a nascadh "
"leis an gcomhéadan seo."

msgid ""
"Interface upon which to listen and to relay. Both PPPoE clients and servers "
"may be connected to this interface."
msgstr ""
"Comhéadan le héisteacht agus le sealaíocht air. Seans go mbeidh cliaint agus "
"freastalaithe PPPoE araon nasctha leis an gcomhéadan seo."

msgid "Invokes <code>pppd</code> with the unit flag"
msgstr "Iarrtar <code>pppd</code> le bratach an aonaid"

msgid "MSS"
msgstr "MSS"

msgid "Max Segment Size"
msgstr "Méid Deighleog Uasta"

msgid "Maximum Sessions"
msgstr "Uasmhéid Seisiúin"

msgid "Maximum concurrent sessions"
msgstr "Uasmhéid seisiúin chomhthráthacha"

msgid "Maximum sessions per peer"
msgstr "Uasmhéid seisiúin in aghaidh an phiara"

msgid "No limit"
msgstr "Gan teorainn"

msgid "No timeout"
msgstr "Gan teorainn ama"

msgid "Offset"
msgstr "Fritháireamh"

msgid "Options file"
msgstr "Comhad roghanna"

msgid "PPP Offset"
msgstr "Fritháireamh PPP"

msgid "PPPoE Relay Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht Leaschraolacháin PPPoE"

msgid "PPPoE Server Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht Freastalaí PPPoE"

msgid "RP PPPoE Relay"
msgstr "Leaschraolacháin RP PPPoE"

msgid "RP PPPoE Server"
msgstr "Freastalaí RP PPPoE"

msgid "Random session selection"
msgstr "Roghnú seisiún randamach"

msgid "Reduces CPU usage, but may cause a race condition on slow CPUs"
msgstr ""
"Laghdaíonn sé úsáid LAP, ach d'fhéadfadh sé a bheith ina chúis le riocht "
"cine ar LAPanna mall"

msgid "Relay Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht Leaschraolacháin"

msgid "Roaring Penguin PPPoE Relay"
msgstr "Sealaíocht PPPoE Penguin Roaring"

msgid "Roaring Penguin PPPoE Server"
msgstr "Freastalaí PPPoE roaring Penguin"

msgid "Server Configuration"
msgstr "Cumraíocht Freastalaí"

msgid "Server Interface"
msgstr "Comhéadan Freastalaí"

msgid "Service Name"
msgstr "Ainm Seirbhíse"

msgid "Synchronous PPP encapsulation"
msgstr "Ionchamhlú PPP sioncrónach"

msgid "Tells the PPPoE server to randomly permute session numbers."
msgstr ""
"Insíonn sé don fhreastalaí PPPoE uimhreacha seisiún a scaipeadh go randamach."

msgid "Timeout"
msgstr "Teorainn ama"

msgid "Unit"
msgstr "Aonad"

msgid "Use Non-UCI Config"
msgstr "Úsáid Cumraíocht Neamh-UCI"

